2002-08-16 Friday 10:07  Roberto Bagnara <bagnara@cs.unipr.it>

	* Watchdog.defs.hh (1.6), Watchdog.inlines.hh (1.5),
	Watchdog.types.hh (1.2), pwl_header.top (1.2): According to the C++
	standard (Section 17.4), every name that starts with an underscore
	is reserved to the implementation.  All the multiple inclusion
	guards have been renamed (some missing ones have been added).

